title: Grateful Dead Live at Cal Expo Amphitheatre on 1990-06-08
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi DR-8 (no Dolby) > Audiophile 2496 >  Wavelab > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC

reviews.review_text: Cal-Expo...6/8/90    I was at these shows...my graduation present just after graduating from The Evergreen State College in Olympia WA. This show had a long first set which rocked. the sound in this smaller venue was great!!! I'm GRATEFUL to yooz heads that captured this show>>>lol to Deadheads everywhere...Scooter.
